<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en" data-theme="light">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Ravina Job Search App</title>
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Instrument+Serif:ital@0;1&family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <style>body{font-family:Inter,Arial,sans-serif;margin:0;background:#f7f6f2;color:#28251d;line-height:1.6}.wrap{max-width:1100px;margin:0 auto;padding:24px}header{padding:56px 0 24px}h1{font-family:"Instrument Serif",Georgia,serif;font-size:clamp(2.5rem,5vw,5rem);line-height:1.05;margin:0 0 16px}h2{font-size:clamp(1.5rem,2vw,2.2rem);margin:0 0 14px}.card{background:#fff;border:1px solid #ddd7cf;border-radius:20px;padding:24px;box-shadow:0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,.06)}.grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(2,minmax(0,1fr));gap:20px}ul{padding-left:18px}table{width:100%;border-collapse:collapse}th,td{padding:12px;border-bottom:1px solid #e7e1d9;text-align:left}th{background:#f3f0ec}a{color:#01696f}.chips{display:flex;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:10px;margin-top:16px}.chip{padding:8px 12px;border-radius:999px;background:#e8f0ef;color:#01696f;font-weight:700;font-size:.9rem}section{padding:18px 0}@media(max-width:850px){.grid{grid-template-columns:1fr}}</style>
</head>
<body>
  <main class="wrap">
    <header>
      <h1>Ravina SearchOS</h1>
      <p>A simple job-search app concept focused on HR roles, direct job links, custom cover letters, and refresh cycles every few hours.</p>
      <div class="chips"><span class="chip">India + remote</span><span class="chip">12 LPA minimum</span><span class="chip">HRBP / HR Ops / HR Generalist</span></div>
    </header>
    <section class="grid">
      <div class="card"><h2>What the app does</h2><ul><li>Refreshes job searches every few hours.</li><li>Ranks roles based on HR fit.</li><li>Generates a custom cover letter for each job.</li><li>Stores direct links to apply quickly.</li></ul></div>
      <div class="card"><h2>Best use case</h2><ul><li>HRBP and HR Generalist roles.</li><li>Operations, employee relations, compliance, dashboards.</li><li>Multinational or structured work environments.</li><li>Fast shortlist and application tracking.</li></ul></div>
    </section>
    <section class="card">
      <h2>Direct links table</h2>
      <table>
        <thead><tr><th>Role</th><th>Source</th><th>Link</th></tr></thead>
        <tbody>
          <tr><td>HR Generalist</td><td>Indeed</td><td><a href="https://in.indeed.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Open</a></td></tr>
          <tr><td>HRBP</td><td>LinkedIn</td><td><a href="https://in.linkedin.com/jobs" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Open</a></td></tr>
          <tr><td>HR Operations Lead</td><td>Naukri</td><td><a href="https://www.naukri.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Open</a></td></tr>
        </tbody>
      </table>
    </section>
  </main>
</body>
</html>
